http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/express/techno/crypto/escrow/wired.html 198.69.72.176 19970216070730 text/html 23779
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 07:07:44 GMT
