<head>
<title>ASG</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Advocates for Self-Government</h1>

<p>The Advocates for Self-Government (ASG, or the Advocates) is an
educational institute. The Advocates publish the <cite>Liberator</cite>
newsletter which is also a catalog of the many outreach and educational
tools they offer.</p>

<p>The Advocates are responsible for the now-famous "World's Smallest
Political Quiz."</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
269 Market Place Blvd. #106, Cartersville, GA 30120<br>
voice: 800-932-1776<br>
web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.self-gov.org/">http://www.self-gov.org/</a><br>
</address>

