<body>

<h1>David Aitken</h1>

<p>David Aitken is a libertarian activist in Colorado.
Aitken served two terms as Chair of the <a
href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpco/index.html">Libertarian Party of
Colorado</a> (as of 1994) and served as State Coordinator for Colorado for the
<a href="/revolution/politics/napm.html">Not a Penny More</a>
campaign. Aitken ran for office in 1996 as a Libertarian.</p>

