<head>
<title>David Bergland</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>David Bergland</h1>

<p>David P. Berland is a prominent Libertarian activist. He was the 1976 vice
presidential candidate and 1984 presidential candidate of the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>.
Bergland was the party's National Chair from 1977 to 1981. Bergland
is the author of <cite>Libertarianism in One Lesson</cite>, a popular
outreach book.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="mailto:DPBergland@aol.com">DPBergland@aol.com</a><br>
</address>

