<head>
<title>Jim Burnes</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Jim Burnes</h1>

<p>Jim Burnes served as State Coordinator for <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/mo/">Missouri</a> for the <a
href="/revolution/politics/napm.html">Not a Penny More</a> campaign.</p>

<p>Contact: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:jburnes@compusci.com">jburnes@compusci.com</a>.</p>

<hr>

<p>Source: Not a Penny More 1993 coordinator list.</p>

