<head>
<title>Gene Cisewski</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Gene Cisewski</h1>

<p>Gene A. Cisewski is a Libertarian activist in the <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/dc/">District of Columbia</a>.
As of 1/96, he is the current chair of the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpdc/">Libertarian Party of
the District of Columbia</a>, National Coordinator of the Libertarian
Party Council of State Chairs, and President & CEO of The Monticello Group.
In January 1996, he was appointed chair of the Logan Circle Community
Development Committee, which oversees zoning and licensing in the downtown
Washington, D.C. neighborhood.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL"]><a
href="mailto:MontiGroup@aol.com">MontiGroup@aol.com</a><br>
