<head>
<title>David Deming</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>David Deming</h1>

<p>David Deming is an
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ok/">Oklahoma</a> libertarian.
Deming is a Ph.D geophysicist and assistant professor of Geology and
Geophysics working at the University of Oklahoma in Norman.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:ddeming@uoknor.edu">ddeming@uoknor.edu</a><br>
</address>

