<head>
<title>EFF</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Electronic Frontier Foundation</h1>

<p>The Electronic Frontier Foundation (EFF) is the premier organization
fighting for online freedom of expression and privacy. EFF was founded
in July 1990 by <a href="/revolution/by_name/K/MitchKapor.html">Mitch Kapor</a>
and <a href="/revolution/by_name/B/JohnBarlow.html">John Perry Barlow</a>.</p>

<p>EFF's first actions were to award a grant to <a
href="/revolution/by_name/C/CPSR.html">Computer Professionals for Social
Responsibility</a> for their Computing and Civil Liberties Project, and to
support two legal cases,
<a href="/revolution/by_name/J/SteveJackson.html">Steve Jackson's</a>
ultimately successful lawsuit against the U.S. government, and a University
of Missouri student's defense against charges of online crime.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
PO Box 170190<br>
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/SanFrancisco.html">San
Francisco</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/">CA</a> 94117<br>
voice: (415) 668-7171<br>
fax: (415) 668-7007<br>
To join EFF, email <img
	src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:membership@eff.org">membership@eff.org</a><br>
For introductory info, send any message to <img
	src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:info@eff.org">info@eff.org</a><br>
Web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.eff.org/">http://www.eff.org/</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/B/JerryBerman.html">Jerry Berman</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/B/JohnBarlow.html">John Perry Barlow</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/G/MatthewGaylor.html">Matthew Gaylor</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/K/MitchKapor.html">Mitch Kapor</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/M/StantonMcCandlish.html">Stanton
	McCandlish</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/W/JimWarren.html">Jim Warren</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/W/SteveWozniak.html">Steve Wozniak</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/techno/exon/eff.html">
	EFF opposes Exon bill</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/techno/crypto/clipper/eff.html">
	EFF opposes Clipper Chip</a></li>
<li><A href="/revolution/express/techno/crypto/clipper/retreat.html">
	White House retreats somewhat from Clipper</a></li>
