<body>

<h1>Tomas Estrada-Palma</h1>

<p>Tomas Estrada-Palma was the
<A href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpva/">Libertarian Party of
Virginia's</a> 1995
candidate for Prince William County Board of Supervisors. Estrada-Palma
is a former Chair of the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpmd/">Libertarian Party of
Maryland</a> and is currently on the board of his Woodbridge housing
association.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
