<head>
<title>Louis Freeh</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Louis Freeh</h1>

<p>Louis J. Freeh is arguably the biggest pig in the entire United States,
which clearly puts him in the running for Mr. World Pig. Freeh is Director
of the Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI).
<A href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/rubyridge/">Ruby Ridge</a>,
<a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/waco/">Waco</a>,
the <a href="/revolution/express/techno/crypto/clipper/">Clipper Chip</a>
and assorted other atrocities have occurred under his faithful watch.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/quotes/">
	FBI Director opposes privacy</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/techno/crypto/clipper/">
	Clipper Chip proposal</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/techno/crypto/clipper/retreat.html">
	White House retreats somewhat from Clipper</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/rubyridge/aftermath.html">
	Aftermath of Ruby Ridge</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/rubyridge/senate.html">
	Senate criticizes federal law enforcement</a></li>
</ul>

