<head>
<title>David Friedman</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>David Friedman</h1>

<p>David Friedman is a Chicago school economist, author and son of Nobel
laureate <a href="/revolution/by_name/F/MiltonFriedman.html">Milton
Friedman</a>. His web page has extensive information about academic
interests and work including the full text of many of his publications.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:DDFr@Best.com">DDFr@Best.com</a><BR>
web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.best.com/~ddfr/">http://www.best.com/~ddfr/</a><br>
</address>

