<head>
<title>Milton Friedman</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Milton Friedman</h1>

<p>Milton Friedman is the Nobel Prize-winning exponent of the Chicago school
of free market economics, also known as the monetarist school.
Friedman supports drug legalization.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/body/drugs/critics/hoover.html">Hoover
	Resolution</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/science/nobel.html">
	Libertarian Nobel Prize winners</a></li>
</ul>

