<head>
<title>Marshal Fritz</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Marshal Fritz</h1>

<p>Marshal Fritz has been a motivational leader in the libertarian movement
for years. Fritz founded the <a href="/revolution/by_name/A/ASG.html">Advocates
for Self-Government</a> and later the <a
href="/revolution/by_name/S/SSSA.html">Separation of School and State
Alliance</a>.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li>none yet
</ul>

