<html>
<head>
<title>Eric Garris</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Eric Garris</h1>

<p>Eric Garris is a longtime libertarian activist. He was a leader in
the Koch-funded (and now long-defunct) Students for a Libertarian Society,
organizing the SLS' National Anti-Draft Demonstrations in 1979. Garris
was a founding member of the Libertarian Party Radical Caucus, and was
state director of the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpca/">Libertarian Party of
California</a>.</p>

<p>After the 1983 Libertarian convention, Garris left the LP to found
the Libertarian Republican Organizing Committee (LROC) (not to be
confused with Republican Liberty Caucus, or the Republican Alliance for
Liberty, or ...).</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:egarris@antiwar.com">egarris@antiwar.com</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li>none yet
</ul>

