<head>
<title>Matthew Gaylor</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Matthew Gaylor</h1>

<p>Matthew Gaylor is a Libertarian activist in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/oh/">Ohio</a>. Gaylor served
as Chair of the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpoh/">Libertarian Party of
Ohio's</a> Central Region (Columbus area) from 1989
to 1993. Since then, he has been Director of the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/B/BLF.html">Buckeye Liberty Foundation</a>,
a libertarian think tank.</p>

<p>Gaylor maintains the <a
href="/revolution/by_name/E/EFF.html">Electronic Frontier Foundation's</a>
Online Activism Resource List.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:freematt@coil.com">freematt@coil.com</a> or
	<img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:freematt@aol.com">freematt@aol.com</a>.<br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
