<head>
<title>Sharon Harris</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Sharon Harris</h1>

<p>Sharon Harris is the third and current President of the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/A/ASG.html">Advocates for Self-Government,
recently selected in 1995.</a></p>

<p>Harris was a founding member of the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpga/">Libertarian Party of
Georgia</a> in
1972 and managed the party's 1988 ballot-status-winning campaigns. She
consulted for <a href="/revolution/by_name/R/CaroleRand.html">Carole Ann
Rand's</a> 1990 campaign for Governor of <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ga/">Georgia</a>. In 1994,
she garnered
over 300,000 votes as candidate for Commissioner of Agriculture.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li>none yet
</ul>

