<head>
<title>Franklin Harris</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Franklin Harris</h1>

<p>Thomas Franklin Harris Jr. is a libertarian activist in Alabama.
At various times, he has been "Critic-at-Large" for <cite>The Exchange:
Culture Reason Style</cite>, described as "North America's Libertarian Culture
Magazine," chair of the Alabama Republican Liberty Caucus, and a
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>
candidate for U.S. House.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:tfharris@hiwaay.net">tfharris@hiwaay.net</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/body/health/forbes.html">
	Forbes' health care innovation</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/philosophy/books.html">
	Books on libertarian philosophy</a></li>
</ul>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
