<head>
<title>Richard Hartman</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Richard Hartman</h1>

<p>Richard L. Hartman is an online firearms rights activist.</p>

<p>Hartman spearheaded the successful "De-Foley-Ate Congress" effort to defeat
anti-gun Speaker of the House Tom Foley in the 1994 elections.</p>

<p>Hartman maintains the <a href="/revolution/by_name/S/SDN.html">Self-Defense
Network</a>.</p>

