<body>

<h1>Friedrich Hayek</h1>

<p>Friedrich A. Hayek was a Nobel Prize-winning Austrian school economist.
He was a student of
<a href="/revolution/by_name/M/LudwigvonMises.html">Ludwig von Mises</a>.</p>

