<body>

<h1>Karl Hess (1923 - 1994)</h1>

<p>Karl Hess was one of the pioneers of the modern libertarian movement.</p>

<p>After his death, the June 1994 <cite>Libertarian Party News</cite> published
several biographical articles in his memory:</p>
<ul>
<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
