<html>

<head>
<title>Hoover Institution</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Hoover Institution</h1>

<p>The Hoover Institution on War, Revolution and Peace is a think tank based
at Stanford University in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/Stanford.html">Stanford</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/">California</a>.</p>

<p>The Institution's "Hoover Resolution" calling for a national commission
on drug policy was signed by many prominent people.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
