<head>
<title>Vaclav Klaus</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Vaclav Klaus</h1>

<p>Vaclav Klaus is the Prime Minister of the <a
href="/revolution/by_place/Europe/CzechRepublic/">Czech Republic</a>. He is
the only
world leader who is an Austrian school economist. Coincidentally enough, the
Czech Republic has economically and culturally outperformed all other former
communist nations and attracts immigrants even from the U.S.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
