<body>

<h1>Eric Klien</h1>

<p>Eric Klien is a libertarian activist in Las Vegas,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nv/">Nevada</a>.</p>

<p>Klien's pledge to contribute $10,000 towards the national debt if the
feds cut spending triggered the Not a Penny More Campaign.</p>

<p>Klien is the guiding force behind the Oceania Project to create a
libertarian floating city.</p>

