<head>
<title>Laissez Faire Books</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Laissez Faire Books</h1>

<p>Laissez Faire Books, established in 1972, publishes a monthly book catalog
including reviews with the widest selection of libertarian books on gun
rights, health care, law, economics, history, Objectivism, philosophy,
environmentalism and other topics.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
942 Howard St.,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/SanFrancisco.html">San
Francisco</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/">CA</a> 94103<br>
Voice: 800-326-0996<br>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:info@LFB.org">info@LFB.org</a><br>
Web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.lfb.org/">http://www.lfb.org/</a><br>
