<body>

<h1>Liberty Tree</h1>

<p><cite>Liberty Tree</cite> is a mail order catalog of books, audio tapes,
video tapes, gifts and collectibles for the free-market conservative and
libertarian movements. It is published by the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/I/Independent.html">Independent Institute</a>.</p>

