<head>
<title>Nancy Lord</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Nancy Lord</h1>

<p>Dr. Nancy Lord, a lawyer and medical doctor, is a Libertarian activist.
Lord was the 1992 vice presidential candidate of the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>. She
often takes on legal cases that involve libertarian principles.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Liberty Defense League, P.O. Box 7223, Macon, Georgia 31209<br>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:defense@mindspring.com">defense@mindspring.com</a><br>
</address>

