<head>
<title>Ludwig von Mises Institute</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Ludwig von Mises Institute</h1>

<p>The Ludwig von Mises Institute is an organization dedicated to furthering
education and research in the Austrian school of economics exemplefied by its
namesake, <a href="/revolution/by_name/M/LudwigvonMises.html">Ludwig von
Mises</a>.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Ludwig Von Mises Institute, Auburn University, Auburn,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/al/">AL</a> 36849<br>
Phone: 205-844-2500<br>
</address>

