<head>
<title>James Madison</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>James Madison</h1>

<p>James Madison was the fourth President of the United States and the
primary author of the U.S. Constitution.</p>

<p>Still, he was a lousy writer. His messages as President were full of
double and triple negatives, contorted clauses and unnecessary fluff.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/quotes/founders.html">
	Founding Fathers' quotes on firearms</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/multi/war/quotes.html">
	Quotes on war</a></li>
</ul>

