<html>
<head>
<title>Peter McWilliams</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Peter McWilliams</h1>

<p>Peter McWilliams is an author of decidedly libertarian bent. His
<cite>Nobody's Fault But Mine: The Absurdity of Consensual Crimes
in a Free Society</cite> is a landmark attack on the restriction of
individual freedom and a celebration of human diversity. His other
topics deal with subjects ranging from the motivational to health.</p>

<p>His web site includes the full text of every book he's ever
published, as well as those in progress!</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:peter@mcwilliams.com">peter@mcwilliams.com</a><br>
web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.mcwilliams.com/">http://www.mcwilliams.com/</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/body/books/">Books on controlling
	your own body</a></li>
</ul>

