<head>
<title>NCARL</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>NCARL</h1>

<p>The National Coalition Against Repressive Legislation (NCARL) is a 30-year
old civil liberties organization defending the right of political
expression.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address> 
<p>NCARL National Office<br>
1313 West 8th Street, Suite 313<br>
Los Angeles, CA 90017<br>
Phone:  (213) 484-6661<br>
FAX:    (213) 484-0266<br>
e-mail: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:ncarl@aol.com">ncarl@aol.com</a></p>

<p>NCARL Washington Office<br>
3321 12th Street NE, 3rd Floor<br>
Washington, D.C. 20017<br>
ATTN:    Kit Gage, Washington Representative<br>
Phone:  (202) 529-4225<br>
FAX:    (202) 526-4611<br>
e-mail: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:kgage@igc.apc.org">kgage@igc.apc.org</a></p>
</address>

