<head>
<title>Thomas Paine</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Thomas Paine</h1>

<p>Thomas Paine was an American Revolutionary and is a libertarian hero.
His <cite>Common Sense</cite> helped motivate American troops (militia)
during tough times. His <cite>Rights of Man</cite> was a libertarian
manifesto.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/community/educate/books/west.html">
	Education and the Industrial Revolution</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/quotes/founders.html">
	Founding Fathers' quotes on firearms</a></li>
</ul>

