<head>
<title>George Phillies</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>George Phillies</h1>

<p>George Phillies is a libertarian activist in Massachusetts. As of
October 1995, he was chair of the Central Massachusetts Libertarian
Association. In 1996, Phillies ran for U.S. Senate in Massachusetts
as a write-in candidate.</p>

