<head>
<title>Thomas Rush</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Thomas Rush</h1>

<p>G. Thomas Rush is Libertarian activist in Texas.
He is a systems engineer with Compaq Computer Corporation based near
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/tx/Houston.html">Houston</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/tx/">Texas</a>.
Rush was National Coordinator of the Not a Penny More campaign,
and has been involved with the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lptx/lpmc/">Libertarian Party
of Montgomery County, Texas</a> since 1993. He has served as its Chair
since September 1994.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:thomasr@bangate.compaq.com">thomasr@bangate.compaq.com</a><br>
</address>

