<head>
<title>Howard Stern</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Howard Stern</h1>

<p>Howard Stern is a nationally syndicate radio shock jock and former
<A href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a> candidate
for governor of
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ny/">New York</a>. Stern
is a staunch defender of free speech, having faced down the Federal
Communications Commission with varying degrees of success.</p>

