<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/election/1996/">
	1996 Libertarian campaigns</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpaz/turmoil.html">
	Turmoil in the Libertarian Party of Arizona</a></li>
</ul>

