<head>
<title>Voters Telecommunications Watch</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Voters Telecommunications Watch</h1>

<p>The Voters Telecommunications Watch (VTW) is an online organization
that monitors proposed U.S. legislation dealing with telecommunications
and the Internet in particular.
VTW has been instrumental in opposing the Clipper Chip and
related proposals.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
<img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:vtw@vtw.org">vtw@vtw.org</a><br>
<img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.vtw.org/">http://www.vtw.org/</a><br>
<img src="/images/gopher.gif" alt="[GOPHER]"><a
	href="gopher://gopher.panix.com/1/vtw/">gopher -p1/vtw
		gopher.panix.com</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li>none yet
</ul>

