<head>
<title>Richard Winger</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Richard Winger</h1>

<p>Richard Winger is the leading expert on ballot access in the United
States. His knowledge of election laws across the states has helped many
third party and independent candidates meet guidelines and challenge
bad laws. Winger, a
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian</a>, is the
publisher of <cite>Ballot Access News</cite>.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:ban@igc.apc.org">ban@igc.apc.org</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<Li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/ballot/conv96.html">
	Moving up the LP convention date</a></li>
</ul>

