<head>
<title>Bill Winter</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Bill Winter</h1>

<p>William Winter is a prominent Libertarian activist. He helped turn the
<a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpnh/">Libertarian Party of
New Hampshire</a> around from a small organization to a
successful political operation with elected and appointed officials.
After his success in <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nh/">New Hampshire</a>,
the <a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a> national
headquarters hired him as Director of Communications.</p>

