<head>
<title>Walter Williams</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Walter Williams</h1>

<p>Walter Williams is a prominent libertarian economist and incendiary
commentator on current affairs. His extensive writings include
<cite>The State Against Blacks</cite>. He also writes a newspaper column
and occasionally guest hosts the Rush Limbaugh show.</p>

<p>Williams currently chairs the economics department of George
Mason University.</p>


