<head>
<title>Browne's '95 Campaigning</title>
<!-- Place: USA -->
<!-- Time: February - September 1995 -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Browne Campaigns Hard in '95</h1>

<p><a href="/revolution/by_name/B/HarryBrowne.html">Harry Browne</a>
began his campaign for the Libertarian presidential nomination
with a strong effort to reach Libertarian Party state conventions across the
country.</p>

<p>Between February and July 1995, Browne appeared at fifteen state conventions:
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/">California</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/co/">Colorado</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ks/">Kansas</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ma/">Massachusetts</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/pa/">Pennsylvania</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/in/">Indiana</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/mn/">Minnesota</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nc/">North Carolina</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/oh/">Ohio</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ky/">Kentucky</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/la/">Louisiana</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/wa/">Washington</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/or/">Oregon</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/tx/">Texas</a>
and <a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/fl/">Florida</a>.</p>

<p>Browne also made four professional appearances during this time, at the 1995
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ga/Atlanta.html">Atlanta</a>
Investment Conference
(<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ga/">Georgia</a>),
the International Assets Advisory Corporation
(<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/fl/">Florida</a>),
the Cascade Institute
(<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/or/">Oregon</a>) and Jim
Blanchard's Gold Investment Conference (California).</p>

<p>July through September '95 saw more state conventions,
including <a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/al/">Alabama</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nh/">New Hampshire</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ct/">Connecticut</a> and
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/wv/">West Virginia</a>.
Browne appeared at the Brass Roots Rally in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/mi/">Michigan</a> and the
Githler Investment Conference in California.</p>

