<h1>Leonard Read</h1>

<p>Leonard Read was one of the few libertarian leaders in the middle twentieth
century. Read founded the <a href="/revolution/by_name/F/FEE.html">Foundation
for Economic Education (FEE)</a>, the oldest active libertarian organization,
in 1946.</p>

