<head>
<title>Firearms</title>
</head>

<body>

<center><a href="http://www.scimitar.com/">
<img src="/revolution/sponsors/scimitar.gif"
alt="SCIMITAR Internet Services"></a></center>

<h1>Firearms</h1>

<img src="revolver.gif" alt="Defense of self and family" align=left>

<p>One of the most fundamental human rights is the right of self-defense:
using whatever means necessary to defend yourself, your family and your
community from violent attack.</p>

<p>Efforts at gun control are <a href="facts/">wrongheaded and doomed to
failure</a>.</p>

<p><a href="enforce/">Enforcement</a> of gun control laws has been incredibly
brutal. <a href="laws/">Laws relating to firearms</a> vary widely from
permissive to restrictive.</p>

<p>Other topics:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="militia/">The citizen militia</a></li>
<li><a href="crime/">Firearms and crime</a></li>
<li><a href="politics/">Politics of firearms (polls, tactics etc.)</a></li>
<li><a href="quotes/">Quotes</a></li>
<li><a href="online/">Online resources</a></li>
<li><a href="humor/">Humor</a></li>
<li><a href="books/">Books</a></li>
<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
href="http://www.lp.org/lp/platform/trtkaba.html">Keep and Bear Arms plank</a>
of the 1994 Libertarian Party Platform</li>
</ul>

