<head>
<title>Testimony of James Wright</title>
<!-- Place: Washington, DC (USA) -->
<!-- Time: testimony March 31, 1995 -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Ten Fundamental Gun Facts</h1>

<p>March 31, 1995 statement of Tulane University criminologist James Wright
before the U.S. House of Representatives Subcommittee on Crime of
the Committee on the Judiciary:</p>

<p><i>Dr. WRIGHT:</i> Thank you so much, and thank you for the opportunity to be
here.  My name is James Wright... and I'm a professor of sociology at Tulane
University.  I've spent the last twenty years of my academic career conducting
research on guns and violence in American society.  In the course of these two
decades, I have come to the conclusion that there are at least ten simple, but
terribly important facts about guns in America that every participant in the
gun control debate should be aware of.  I have referred to these in a recent
paper as "Ten Essential Observations on Guns in America," and my point is to
share them with the Committee today.</p>

<p> While many of the facts of the gun control issue are hotly contested, and
matters of great dispute, the ten fundamental truths that I wish to discuss are
matters about which everyone more or less agrees.</p>

<ol>
<li><a href="households.html">Half of U.S. households own guns</a>
<li><a href="circulation.html">200,000,000 firearms are in the U.S. now</a>
<li><a href="sport.html">Most guns are owned for recreation</a>
<li><a href="defense.html">Many guns are owned for defense against crime</a>
<li><a href="retail.html">Bad guys don't buy guns through retail channels</a>
<li><a href="violence.html">Bad guys carry guns for surviving violent world</a>
<li><a href="law.html">Bad guys indifferent to existing gun control laws</a>
<li><a href="demand.html">Demand for guns creates its own supply</a>
<li><a href="evil.html">Guns are not inherently good or evil</a>
<li><a href="culture.html">Guns are part of the American culture</a>
</ol>
 
<p>And, thank you so much for your attention.  Dr. Bordua...</p>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
