	FBI bugged Mt.Carmel during siege (DMN 4/21/93)
	Davidians on 3/14/93 flashed "SOS SOS SOS FBI BROKE NEGOTIATIONS"
		with light beacon (AP), then FBI used stadium lights/tanks
		to block view of signal;
	FBI said they planned to knock down Davidians' ham radio station
