http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/firearms/enforce/lamplugh.html 198.69.72.176 19970216052413 text/html 10398
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 05:24:27 GMT
