<head>
<title>Tulsa, Oklahoma</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Tulsa,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ok/">Oklahoma</a>
(<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/">USA</a>)</h1>

<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/note.html">
	December 1991: BATF Wrecks House, Leaves Note</a></li>
</ul>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
<a href="/revolution/">Topics</a> -
<a href="/revolution/by_place/">Places</a> -
