<head>
<title>The Waco Raid</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>BATF Used Excessive Force at Waco</h1>

<p>The BATF merely had a warrant to search the Davidians' residence for
unregistered weapons. They did not have an arrest warrant for anyone,
and they certainly did not have a
use-overwhelming-military-force-against-US-citizens warrant.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="opportunity.html">BATF had opportunity to search or arrest
	Davidians peacefully</a></li>
<li><a href="gunfire.html">BATF agents may have fired illegally from
	helicopters</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/waco/victims.html">Branch
	Davidians who died in the attack</a></li>
</ul>

