http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/firearms/enforce/waco/trial/atf.html 198.69.72.176 19970216064231 text/html 23918
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 06:42:43 GMT
