http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/firearms/enforce/waco/reaction/hearings.html 198.69.72.176 19970216064818 text/html 11104
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 06:48:30 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 10932
Last-modified: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 19:37:17 GMT
