<head>
<title>Jealous Husband Killed</title>
<!-- Place: June 28, 1995 -->
<!-- Time: Spokane, Washington (USA) -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Jealous Husband Killed</h1>

<p>Thinking he would catch his wife cheating, "Skip" Elsom burst into
Stan Parker's
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/wa/Spokane.html">Spokane</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/wa/">Washington</a> apartment
just after midnight with a
camera, baseball bat and .45 pistol.</p>

<p>Elsom burst into Parker's bedroom, snapped a photograph, raised the
baseball bat and began shooting his pistol, hitting Parker three times.
Parker, a firearms collector, returned fire with a 9mm semiautomatic
handgun, hitting Elsom in the chest. Elsom fled, collapsed on the sidewalk
and died.</p>

<p>Parker was sleeping alone.</p>

<hr>

<p>Source: June 1995 post to the <a
href="/revolution/by_name/S/SDN.html">Self-Defense Network</a>.</p>

