<html>
<head>
<title>Books on Politics</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Books on Politics</h1>

<h2><cite>The Political Racket</cite></h2>

Martin L. Gross' <cite>The Political Racket: Deceit, Self-Interest, and
Corruption in American Politics</cite> is "chock full of ammunition for
pointing out how wasteful, inept and corrupt the current government is,"
according to Brooke Anderson (<img src="/images/mail.gif"
alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:brooke@alumni.caltech.edu">brooke@alumni.caltech.edu</a>).</p>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
