<head>
<title>Vegas and D.C.</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Difference Between Vegas and D.C.</h1>

<p>The difference between Las Vegas and
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/dc/">Washington, D.C.</a>,
is that in Vegas, the drunks are gambling with their <em>own</em> money.</p>

