<head>
<title>Porcupines and Capitol Hill</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Porcupines and Capitol Hill</h1>

<p>The difference between a porcupine and Capitol Hill is that a porcupine
has pricks on the <em>outside</em>.</p>

