<head>
<title>'Politics' Origin</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Origin of Word 'Politics'</h1>

<p>The word 'politics' comes from the Greek 'poly' meaning 'many', and
'tics' of course are bloodsucking parasites.</p>

<p>-- 1992 Libertarian presidential candidate <a
href="/revolution/by_name/M/AndreMarrou.html">Andre Marrou</a></p>

