<body>

<h1>Moderated Libertarian Lists</h1>

<p>In September 1995, <a href="/revolution/by_name/L/MikeLinksvayer.html">Mike
Linksvayer</a> started two moderated mailing lists
for libertarians. "News" is for announcements of a general nature
and "news-online" is for announcement of new online resources.</p>

<p>Both lists are available in reflected or digest formats. Digests are
sent out once weekly.</p>

<p>To subscribe, send email with the subject line "subscribe" to:</p>
<ul>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news-request@libertarian.com">news-request@libertarian.com</a></li>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news-digest-request@libertarian.com">news-digest-request@libertarian.com</a></li>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news-online-request@libertarian.com">news-online-request@libertarian.com</a></li>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news-online-digest-request@libertarian.com">news-online-digest-request@libertarian.com</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Send submissions to:</p>
<ul>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news@libertarian.com">news@libertarian.com</a></li>
<li><img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:news-online@libertarian.com">news-online@libertarian.com</a></li>
</ul>

