<A href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/az/Phoenix.html">Phoenix</a>,
	<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/az/">Arizona</a>,
	City Council</li>
<li>Austin Lett, 16% for Chatham,
	<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nj/">New Jersey</a>,
	Township Committee</li>
